HEADWORD: Feline
<hw>Fe"line</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>felinus</ets>, fr. <ets>feles</ets>, <ets>felis</ets>, cat, prob.
orig., the fruitful: cf. F. <ets>f⟦eacute⟧lin</ets>. See
